'''基斯杜化·羅拔·"基斯"·伊維路莫'''（{{lang-en|'''Christopher Robert "Chris" Iwelumo'''}}，{{bd|1978年|8月1日|catidx=Iwelumo, Chris}}）是一名[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]裔前[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]。身材高大的伊維路莫是傳統英式的柱躉中鋒，於效力[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]、[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]、[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]及[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]期間分別協助球隊成功取得升班資格。

==生平==
===早年===
伊維路莫的父親是[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]人，而母親則為[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]人<ref name="Chris Iwelumo in surprise call-up for Scotland">{{cite news | language = en | first = Graham | last = Spiers | title = Chris Iwelumo in surprise call-up for Scotland | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/scotland/article4870258.ece | publisher = ''The Times'' | date = 2008-10-03 | accessdate = 2008-10-23 | location = London | archive-date = 2021-02-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210216025123/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/ }}</ref>，他於1996年加入當時仍在[[蘇甲|蘇甲]]參賽的[[圣米伦足球俱乐部|聖美倫]]作為學徒球員展開其足球事業。

伊維路莫僅為聖美倫上陣19場，演出未有獲得注目，在對[[伯威克流浪足球會|伯威克]]（Berwick Rangers）的[[蘇格蘭聯賽盃|蘇格蘭聯賽盃]]<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/aberdeen/victory-is-taylor-made-1.441300 |title=Victory is Taylor made |publisher=Herald Scotland |date=13 August 1996 |accessdate=14 February 2010}}</ref>，及[[邓迪足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:邓迪; zh-hk:登地;}-]]的[[蘇格蘭足總盃|蘇格蘭足總盃]]賽事各射入1球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/aberdeen/kamikaze-comeback-ends-in-tears-for-nine-man-saints-1.357868 |title=Kamikaze comeback ends in tears for nine-man Saints |publisher=Herald Scotland |date=25 January 1998 |accessdate=14 February 2010}}</ref>。 1998年年初，[[丹麥|丹麥]]低級別球隊[[Aarhus_Fremad|阿曉斯費馬]]（Aarhus Fremad）羅致伊維路莫，直到兩年後的2000年2月才棄用。伊維路莫首先到[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]跟隨[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英乙〈第三級〉]]的[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]試訓，其後獲得另一支英乙球隊[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]賞識，動筆簽署四年合約。

===史篤城===
經歷兩年在[[丹麥|丹麥]]的磨練，伊維路莫加盟英乙的史篤城，由於1999/00年球季僅餘1個月，他只獲派在4場賽事的末段後補登場，包括2000年4月16日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]舉行的[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]決賽，史篤城以2-1擊敗[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]第二度奪標。

2000/01年球季伊維路莫有良好的開始，於2000年8月22日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一圈首回合作客5-1大破[[約克城足球會|約克城]]射入加盟後首個入球；10月21日聯賽對[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:米尔沃尔; zh-hk:米禾爾;}-]]，他在83分鐘才後補進場，於完場前射入奠勝球協助球隊以3-2獲勝。他於11月10日被外借到當時處身[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英丙〈第四級〉]]的[[約克城足球會|約克城]]三個月，期間合共上陣16場及射入3球，包括聯賽兩戰[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:马科斯菲尔德; zh-hk:馬爾斯菲;}-]]各入1球，另1球在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]時射入。翌年2月借用期滿後隨即再被借到另一支英丙球隊[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]一個月，期間上陣4場，於首場對[[曼斯菲尔德城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:曼斯菲尔德城; zh-hk:曼斯菲;}-]]射入1球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/1166756.stm |title=Mansfield 2–1 Cheltenham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=13 February 2001 }}</ref>。

2001/02年球季伊維路莫在史篤城取得較多上陣機會，惟仍不是隊中的常規正選，他在2001年10月21日於「波特里斯德比」（Potteries Derby）對[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:韦尔港; zh-hk:維爾港;}-]]為球隊射入扳平1-1。2002年3月伊維路莫延長兩年合約<ref name="Iwelumo extends contract">{{cite news |language=en | title = Iwelumo extends contract | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/1853582.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2002-03-04 | accessdate = 2007-09-22}}</ref>。史篤城以第5位結束球季獲得參加升班附加賽資格，伊維路莫以正選身份參賽全部3場附加賽，準決賽對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]兩回合累計2-2，[[加時賽|加時賽]]險勝3-2晉級，2002年5月11日決賽在[[千禧球場|千禧球場]]對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布伦特福德; zh-hk:賓福特;}-]]，史篤城以2-0獲勝，來屆升班上[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英甲〈第二級〉]]。伊維路莫在各項賽事合共上陣47場及射入個人新高的12球。

升班後史篤城只能在聯賽榜下游掙扎，2002/03年球季伊維路莫上陣36場仍有7球斬獲。翌季史篤城前鋒加入[[艾迪·艾堅比耶|艾迪·艾堅比耶]]後有人滿之患，而伊維路莫在季初僅在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|羅奇代爾]]射入1球，他上陣機會日漸減少，上半季僅獲派上陣11場，因而與史篤城協議加入轉會名單<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3354575.stm |title=Stoke sign Svard on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-12-29 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307014145/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3354575.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，史篤城向友會求售，[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:巴恩斯利; zh-hk:班士利;}-]]一度表示有興趣<ref name="Barnsley eye Iwelumo">{{cite news | language = en | title = Barnsley eye Iwelumo | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/3376253.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2004-01-07 | accessdate = 2007-09-22 | archive-date = 2004-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040319171602/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/3376253.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2004年1月13日伊維路莫為史篤城在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]上陣對[[溫布頓足球會|溫布頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/3385215.stm |title=Stoke 0-1 Wimbledon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-01-13 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307164448/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/3385215.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦是他最後一次披上史篤城球衣。3月15日伊維路莫獲外借到英乙〈第三級〉的[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]直至球季結束<ref name="Iwelumo moves to Albion">{{cite news | language = en | title = Iwelumo moves to Albion | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/3513322.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2004-03-15 | accessdate = 2007-09-22 | archive-date = 2004-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040405201840/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/3513322.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，期間上陣10場及射入4球，協助球隊取得第4位參加升班附加賽，伊維路莫再次以正選身份出席3場附加賽，首先在準決賽對[[斯温登足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯温登; zh-hk:史雲頓;}-]]，兩回合加時後累計仍然2-2平手，[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]4-3淘汰對手，5月30日決賽在[[千禧球場|千禧球場]]對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]，離完場尚餘8分鐘，伊維路莫在禁區內被敵衛撞跌獲判[[十二碼|十二碼]]，由隊友[[Leon_Knight|萊昂·奈特]]（Leon Knight）一針見血射入奠定勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/3750777.stm |title=Bristol City 0-1 Brighton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-05-30 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923190712/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/3750777.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。借用期滿返回史篤城後遭放棄，結束四年長的賓主關係。

===由德國到查爾頓===
白禮頓與伊維路莫商討加盟條件<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3775497.stm |title=Seagulls move to keep stars |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-06-04 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307095348/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3775497.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，雖然獲提供兩年合約，但他拒絕簽約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3878285.stm |title=Albion search for striker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-07-08 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310100358/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3878285.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終於2004年7月12日以[[自由球員|自由身]]加盟[[德乙|德乙]]的[[亚琛足球俱乐部|亞琛]]<ref name="Iwelumo joins Aachen">{{cite news | language = en | title = Iwelumo joins Aachen | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3888139.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2004-07-12 | accessdate = 2007-09-22 | archive-date = 2004-07-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040715035812/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/3888139.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但他在[[德國|德國]]僅逗留了一季，於9次後補上陣後被放棄。2005年7月6日伊維路莫加盟[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]<ref name="Colchester complete Iwelumo deal">{{cite news |language=en | title = Colchester complete Iwelumo deal | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/4655015.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2005-07-06 | accessdate = 2007-09-22}}</ref>，在新球隊他重拾射門鞋，於2005/06年球季上陣55場，射入19球，協助高車士打取得聯賽亞軍，來屆升班[[英冠|英冠]]。翌季伊維路莫繼續出色的表現，於2008年11月28日在聯賽5-1大勝[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:赫尔城; zh-hk:侯城;}-]]中，個人射入4球糊出「大四喜」<ref name="Colchester 5-1 Hull">{{cite news | language = en | title = Colchester 5–1 Hull | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6183358.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2006-11-29 | accessdate = 2007-09-22 | archive-date = 2017-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170816060929/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6183358.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，最終上陣48場及射入18球，而高車士打亦取得聯賽第10位，是球會歷來聯賽最高的排名。

伊維路莫與高車士打未能就續約達成協議<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/6676057.stm |title=Iwelumo turns down new contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-21 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2019-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827164037/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/6676057.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於季後約滿回復自由身<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/6624035.stm |title=Iwelumo keeping his options open |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-04 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307082047/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/6624035.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2007年5月21日加盟剛降班[[英冠|英冠]]的[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]<ref name="Charlton snap up Varney & Iwelumo">{{cite news | language = en | title = Charlton snap up Varney & Iwelumo | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/charlton_athletic/6676699.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2007-05-21 | accessdate = 2007-05-21 | archive-date = 2007-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071009122555/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/charlton_athletic/6676699.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]伊維路莫出席查爾頓的全部46場聯賽，並以10個入球成為球隊首席射手。他更獲選「[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽#每月最佳球員|11月英冠最佳球員]]」，期間射入3球，包括連續兩場在完場射入唯一入球，分別絕殺[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:南安普顿; zh-hk:修咸頓;}-]]及[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = Charlton star takes monthly award | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/charlton_athletic/7126729.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2007-12-04 | accessdate = 2008-07-12 | archive-date = 2007-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071206120052/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/charlton_athletic/7126729.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===狼隊===
伊維路莫獲准季後離開查爾頓作為球隊節省開支措施的一部分，他於2008年7月14日簽署兩年合約加盟同屬[[英冠|英冠]]的[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en | title = Iwelumo completes Wolves switch | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7505174.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2008-07-14 }}</ref>，他需要與[[安迪·基奧治|基奧治]]、[[森·禾基斯|-{zh-hans:沃科斯; zh-hk:禾基斯;}-]]和[[西尔万·埃班克斯-布莱克|-{zh-hans:埃班克斯-布莱克; zh-hant:比歷克;}-]]競爭正選前鋒席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7542772.stm |title=Iwelumo ready to fight for place |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-05 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307151052/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7542772.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊維路莫在8月9日首披狼隊戰衣出戰[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:普利茅斯; zh-hk:普利茅夫;}-]]；三天後在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]梅開二度才於[[加時賽|加時賽]]以3-2驚險地淘汰[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:艾宁顿; zh-hk:阿克寧頓;}-]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7542020.stm |title=Wolves 3-2 Accrington (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-12 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2020-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200415045328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7542020.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；8月16日回到聯賽再中兩元以4-1反勝[[谢周三足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢周三; zh-hk:錫周三;}-]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7551200.stm |title=Wolves 4-1 Sheff Wed |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-16 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213732/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7551200.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；季初狀態大勇的伊維路莫入球停不了，主場大勝[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:诺丁汉森林;zh-hk:諾定咸森林;}-]]5-1又入1球，協助球隊進佔聯賽榜首<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7578476.stm |title=Wolves 5-1 Nottm Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-30 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806134743/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7578476.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；9月20日作客3-1擊敗[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]伊維路莫包辦球隊全部三球，以一記美妙[[倒掛|倒掛]]先開紀錄，其後下半場在門前射入，並於72分鐘射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]完成[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，開季7場射入8球，但4分鐘後卻因用頭撞敵衛而被球證直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en | title = Preston 1–3 Wolves | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7613993.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2008-09-20 | accessdate = 2008-09-20}}</ref>，賽後被侵犯的[[Seán_St_Ledger|肖·圣雷德格]]（Seán St Ledger）向球證解釋事件純屬意外，為此狼隊對紅牌判決提出上訴，但[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]維持原判，伊維路莫停賽3場<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = FA reject Wolves' Iwelumo appeal | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7629282.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2008-09-24 | accessdate = 2010-09-14 | archive-date = 2008-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080925064240/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7629282.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。停賽仍然無阻伊維路莫的表現，復出後再射入7球，其中在11月6場賽事射入6球，使他再獲選為「[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽#每月最佳球員|11月英冠最佳球員]]」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Iwelumo is Championship's Top Man |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/ChampionshipPlayeroftheMonth/0,,10794~1481139,00.html |publisher=''The Football League'' |date=2008-12-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211072947/http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/ChampionshipPlayeroftheMonth/0%2C%2C10794~1481139%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-12-11 |accessdate=2010-09-14 }}</ref>，連續兩年在11月份獲獎。但自此他卻經歷16場的入球荒，直到2009年3月14日才在舊東家查爾頓身上再取得入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7946470.stm |title=Iwelumo delighted to end drought |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-16 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310125336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7946470.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他的球季卻在4月6日對升班競爭對手[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]時提早結束，對方[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[Lee_Carsley|卡斯利]]（Lee Carsley）一記凶狠攔截換來一面[[紅牌|紅牌]]，而伊維路莫則需用擔架抬離場<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = Birmingham 2–0 Wolves | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7972882.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2009-04-06 | accessdate = 2010-09-14 | archive-date = 2009-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090407011747/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7972882.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他因[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[韌帶|韌帶]]受傷而缺席餘下5場賽事，最終狼隊維持強勢奪得聯賽冠軍，獲得直接升班[[英超|英超]]資格<ref>{{cite news| language = en| title = Barnsley 1–1 Wolves| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8001872.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-04-25| accessdate = 2010-09-14| archive-date = 2017-08-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170827220527/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8001872.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

休季後伊維路莫傷勢復原，但他在對[[澳洲|澳洲]]球隊[[珀斯光荣足球俱乐部|珀斯光輝]]的首場季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]再度受傷，這次蹠骨[[骨折|骨折]]，錯過季初的賽事<ref>{{cite news | language=en | title = Wolves' Iwelumo breaks metatarsal | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8144655.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2009-07-10}}</ref>。伊維路莫養傷直到2009年9月29日復出參加半場的預備隊賽事<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8283288.stm |title=Iwelumo targets first-team return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-30 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307044345/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8283288.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於10月24日在對[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]才正式參加首場[[英超|英超]]賽事，但在下場對[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]時再度觸傷蹠骨舊患而休戰1個月<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = Iwelumo suffers injury setback | url = http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5676383,00.html | publisher = Sky Sports | date = 2009-11-05 | accessdate = 2010-09-14 | archive-date = 2016-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160903232305/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5676383,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。當再次康復後，狼隊單前鋒陣式的正選席位，已由在夏季以破球會紀錄身價加盟的[[凯文·道尔|-{zh-hans:凯文·道尔;zh-hant:奇雲·杜爾}-]]長期佔據，伊維路莫只能獲得零星後補上陣機會。2010年2月13日伊維路莫獲緊急借用到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]1個月爭取上陣時間<ref>{{cite news | language=en | title = Bristol City sign Wolves striker Chris Iwelumo| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bristol_city/8514105.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2010-02-13}}</ref>，期間上陣7場，在對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:西布罗姆维奇; zh-hk:西布朗;}-]]及[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]各入1球。借用期滿後返回狼隊努力爭取出戰機會，僅再在[[英超|英超]]賽場上取得7場後補上陣，雖然最終狼隊能夠護級成功，但他沒有取得任何入球，表示在近18個月為狼隊上陣僅射入1球。

===般尼===
2010年6月1日伊維路莫動筆簽約加盟剛降回[[英冠|英冠]]的[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，合約為期兩年，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{citeweb |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8716685.stm |title=Burnley snap up Wolves striker Chris Iwelumo |date=2010-06-01 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402031836/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8716685.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月7日首次披甲主場迎戰[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:诺丁汉森林;zh-hk:諾定咸森林;}-]]，他在完半場前插水式頂入唯一入球，帶領球隊旗開得勝<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8881382.stm |title=Burnley 1-0 Nott'm Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-07 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531102729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8881382.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；9月11日伊維路莫演出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，協助球隊4-3反勝[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8977578.stm |title=Burnley 4-3 Preston |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-09-11 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125191808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8977578.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===屈福特===
2011年7月19日伊維路莫轉投另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，簽約兩年，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14200193.stm |title=Watford sign striker Chris Iwelumo from Burnley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-19 |accessdate=2011-07-20 |archive-date=2011-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906052119/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14200193.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，穿上離隊的上屆英冠神射手[[丹尼·格拉咸|-{zh-hans:丹尼·格雷厄姆; zh-hk:丹尼·格拉咸;}-]]遺下的「10」號球衣。

