2012年11月13日，[[英甲|英甲]]球隊[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]從[[英冠|英冠]][[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]借用伊維路莫至2013年1月1日<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = Notts County sign Watford striker Chris Iwelumo on loan | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20463386 | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2012-11-13 | accessdate = 2013-06-04 | archive-date = 2013-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017212056/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20463386 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

