==國家隊==
伊維路莫於2002年首次獲[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]徵召遠征[[南韓|南韓]]，但因所屬的[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]參賽升班附加賽而被迫退隊。直到2007年11月他獲挑選代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表乙隊|蘇格蘭B隊]][[友賽|友賽]]愛爾蘭B隊<ref name="Scotland B squad announced">{{cite news | language = en | title = Scotland B squad announced | url = http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news.cfm?newsid=3363 | publisher = [[蘇格蘭足球總會|蘇格蘭足球總會]] | date = 2007-11-09 | accessdate = 2008-07-14 | archive-date = 2008-03-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080317020059/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news.cfm?newsid=3363 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，被派在這場1-1和局賽事中上陣<ref name="Scotland B 1-1 Rep of Ireland B">{{cite news | language = en | title = Scotland B 1–1 Rep of Ireland B | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7100835.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2007-11-20 | accessdate = 2008-07-14 | archive-date = 2007-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071122091748/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7100835.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。伊維路莫再獲國家隊徵召備戰[[2010年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|世界盃外圍賽]]在2008年10月11日舉行主場對[[挪威國家足球隊|挪威]]的賽事<ref>{{cite news | language = en | title = First Scotland call for Iwelumo | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7648194.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2008-10-02 | accessdate = 2008-10-02 | archive-date = 2008-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081005044308/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7648194.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，他於57分鐘後補首次登場，賽事以0-0和局收場，但他在離門3碼面對空門射失卻成為賽後談論焦點<ref name="Scotland 0-0 Norway">{{cite news | language = en | title = Scotland 0–0 Norway | url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7654327.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date = 2008-10-11 | accessdate = 2008-10-11 | archive-date = 2019-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827201259/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7654327.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

